These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Hobby: hiking, fishing, skydiving, rock-climbing
Sport: skateboarding, baseball, basketball, surfing
1. Hobby:skydiving is between Sport:basketball and Sport:baseball##2
2. Hobby:rock-climbing is on the left or right of Sport:basketball##3
3. Sport:basketball is not to the left of Sport:basketball##8
4. Sport:baseball != Hobby:skydiving##6
5. Hobby:skydiving is somewhere to the right of Hobby:hiking##5
6. Hobby:hiking is on the right of Sport:skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | hiking | skydiving | fishing  |
| Sport   | skateboarding | basketball   | surfing  | baseball |

