.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Food: broccoli, eggplant, apricot, peach
Job: coach, firefighter, social-worker, police-officer
1. Job:police-officer is not to the left of Job:police-officer##8
2. Food:broccoli is somewhere to the right of Food:peach##5
3. Food:broccoli == Job:firefighter##1
4. Food:peach is between Food:broccoli and Food:eggplant##2
5. Food:eggplant is somewhere between Food:apricot and Job:coach##7
6. Job:social-worker is somewhere to the left of Food:eggplant##5
7. Job:coach is not to the left of Job:coach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | apricot | eggplant          | peach | broccoli     |
| Job    | social-worker      | police-officer | coach | firefighter |

