.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Job: entrepreneur, software-developer, musician, writer
Movie-Genre: western, scientific, zombie, disaster
1. Movie-Genre:western is not to the left of Job:musician##8
2. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the far left##1
3. Job:software-developer is on the right of Job:entrepreneur##1
4. Job:software-developer is in an even position##4
5. Job:writer is on the far left or far right##3
6. Job:entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of Movie-Genre:disaster##5
7. Job:writer == Movie-Genre:zombie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | entrepreneur | software-developer | musician     | writer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific    | disaster   | western | zombie    |

