.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
Music-Genre: house, r&b, techno, gospel
Sport: rowing, skiing, snowboarding, basketball
1. Sport:skiing is on the left of Sport:basketball##1
2. Sport:rowing is not to the left of Sport:skiing##8
3. Sport:snowboarding is on the right of Music-Genre:r&b##1
4. Music-Genre:gospel is not to the right of Sport:snowboarding##8
5. Music-Genre:house == Sport:rowing##1
6. Music-Genre:house is on the right of Sport:snowboarding##1
7. Music-Genre:techno is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | r&b         | gospel   | house    |
| Sport         | skiing | basketball | snowboarding | rowing |

