4. Movie-Genre:adventure is not to the left of Sport:golf##8
5. Sport:golf is somewhere between Movie-Genre:action and Sport:basketball##7
6. Sport:basketball is somewhere to the right of Movie-Genre:martial-arts##5
7. Sport:basketball is not to the left of Movie-Genre:thriller##8
