4. Music-Genre:techno is on the left or right of Music-Genre:electronic##3
5. Food:mango is somewhere to the left of Food:grapes##5
6. Food:pomegranate is not to the left of Music-Genre:r&b##8
7. Food:pomegranate == Music-Genre:r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
