2. Transport:quad-bike is on the far left##1
3. Transport:quad-bike is on the left or right of Music-Genre:reggae##3
4. Music-Genre:punk is somewhere to the right of Transport:train##5
5. Transport:motorbike == Transport:motorbike##1
6. Music-Genre:house != Transport:helicopter##6
7. Music-Genre:hip-hop is not to the right of Music-Genre:house##8
8. Transport:train is not to the left of Transport:motorbike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | reggae | house | punk |
| Transport     | quad-bike | motorbike       | train  | helicopter    |

