4. Pet:dog == Transport:airplane##1
5. Pet:goat is somewhere between Transport:boat and Transport:airplane##7
6. Pet:goat is on the left of Pet:cat##1
7. Transport:bike is between Transport:train and Pet:dog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | goldfish    | goat | cat | dog |
| Transport   | boat | train      | bike     | airplane     |

 